On I-90 between milepost 148 and 165 (George to Moses Lake) Monday through Friday from 6 a.m. to 6 p.m. expect lane closures and reduced speed where the contractor is paving at grind out locations. I-90 Paving East of George #9638County: Grant Highway: I-90 Region: North CentralLocation: MP 148-165Description: This section of roadway is due for resurfacing by the least life cycle cost method. This project will plane and pave the existing roadway with hot mix asphalt paving. This will prolong the life of the roadway and provide for a smoother surface for the public.
